summaries.short: Frances discovers Robert has hired a lawyer, and responds in kind; Frances looks to connect with an influential artist.
summaries.full: Robert discovers his lawyer's experience doesn't align with his current needs. Blindsided when she learns that her husband already has legal representation, Frances opens up a little too much in her initial meeting with Max Brodkin, a seasoned midtown divorce lawyer. Diane, Dallas and Frances head to an influential artist's show in hopes that Frances will make a connection.
